KodeKloud Exam Tip

When a task says:

"Allocate a Public IP address named devops-pip"

The minimum command required is:

az network public-ip create \
  --resource-group <RG_NAME> \
  --name devops-pip

Then verify:

az network public-ip list -o table

If you see:

devops-pip   Succeeded

the task is complete. ✅
